&lt;li&gt;4+ years working in analytics / data science, preferably at a start-up or a technology-focused healthcare company.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of hands-on experience performing analysis and complex data transformations with SQL.&lt;/li&gt;
